text: Dick de Man (16 May 1909 - 3 July 1996) was a Dutch swimmer. He competed in the men's 1500 metre freestyle event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1909 births Category:1996 deaths Category:Dutch male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of the Netherlands Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Utrecht (city)
